# an interactive process monitor
-d N	the time interval between update, default as 5s.
-b	run top in batch mode
-n N	usually used with -b together, specify the number of execution
-p PID	look at the specified PID

commands used for top:
1	    show different CPU
<space>	    refresh contents
h|?	    help
m	    memory 
t	    process and CPU status
c	    commands and complete commands
M	    sort by occupied memory size
P	    sort by CPU usage
q	    quit
r	    renice
